'''Deputy Hall''' is a deputy at Tri-County Hospital, on the prison floor.

==History==
Desuty Hall greeted [[Amanda Joseph]] and the doctors as they entered the hospital prison. She led them to [[Kristen Rochester|Kristen Rochester's]] cell. She unlocked the door to let the doctors in and stayed with them throughout their time with her, first restraining her when she attacked Dr. Eldredge and later removing the restraints during Kristen's labor under Eldredge's orders.

==Career==
She is a deputy at Tri-County Hospital on the prison floor.
